And now, you know, like, I hit the book

00:06:14.180 --> 00:06:16.790
mark button, and I've got a game installed, because

00:06:16.790 --> 00:06:18.240
they can just like, go find it.

00:06:18.410 --> 00:06:21.820
And then you could have like, some local curation of

00:06:21.820 --> 00:06:22.260
